import React from 'react'
import { FormContainer, Input, Button } from './styles'

function Form() {
  return (
    <FormContainer>
        <Input 
        value = ''
        type = 'text'
        role = 'input'
        />
        <Button type = "submit">Add</Button>
    </FormContainer>
  )
}

export default Form
